Compress the configuration file and store the compressed version in the ConfigMap.
When you mount the ConfigMap in your Blackbox Exporter Pod, run an init container to decompress the configuration file before the main container starts.
https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/STXKQY_CSI_SHR/com.ibm.spectrum.scale.csi.v1r00.doc/pdf/scale_csi.pdf
apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: my-configmap
data:
  my-config.conf: ${MY_CONFIG_CONTENT}
export MY_CONFIG_CONTENT="$(< my-config.conf)"
envsubst < configmap-template.yaml > configmap.yaml
